snippet.title: Philistine Ploy for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Philistine Ploy is a graphical text-adventure set in Judea.


What I think:

While not horrendous, it isn't a good game at all...it is kinda boring and you encounter the Philistines way to often....
